description: Penthouse Living at Trimount Place! Experience elevated living in this south-facing penthouse at Trimount Place—featuring spectacular direct water views and an expansive 822 sq. ft. private deck perfect for sunrises, sunsets, and al fresco entertaining. Designed to inspire and built to last, this residence boasts 5” white oak floors, Calacatta Colorado quartz countertops, and custom shaker cabinetry in a refined mix of white and light grey. The kitchen is outfitted with sleek Bosch appliances and a La Belle Air ceramic backsplash, while the spa-inspired bathrooms offer porcelain shower walls and Carrara marble mosaic floors. The oversized walk-in closet is a true luxury—designed to fit even the most extensive wardrobe. Enjoy resort-style amenities including roof decks, a sky lounge, fitness center, pet spa, and more. Plus, the developer is offering an interest RATE BUY-DOWN to make this dream home even more attainable.Schedule your private tour today!
